</li>
<li class="links ">
<a href="power-wireless.html.te" title="Switch off unused wireless technologies">Switch off unused wireless technologies</a><span class="desc"> — Bluetooth, wi-fi and mobile broadband can be switched off to reduce battery use.</span>
